cast.overview: Set more than a decade after the events of the first film, learn the story of the Sully family (Jake, Neytiri, and their kids), the trouble that follows them, the lengths they go to keep each other safe, the battles they fight to stay alive, and the tragedies they endure.
cast.title: Avatar: The Way of Water

details.biography: Evans started acting at 3 years old. He is the fourth child of six siblings. He is of Maori, Tahitian, and mixed European descent and speaks fluent Maori. His iwi (tribe) associations are the Ngati Whaatua and Nga Puhi, with sub tribes Ngati Hine, Ngati Kahu and Te Aupouri.
details.name: Duane Evans Jr.
